# ==========================================
# VoiceSnap 极简 .gitignore (仅保留核心源码)
# ==========================================

# 1. 默认忽略所有文件
*

# 2. 允许特定的根目录文件
!LICENSE
!README.md
!screenshot.png
!.gitignore

# 3. 允许特定的源码目录及其内容
!VoiceSnap.Engine/
!VoiceSnap.Engine/**
!VoiceSnapWPF/
!VoiceSnapWPF/**

# 4. 在允许的目录中，重新忽略不需要的产物
**/bin/
**/obj/
**/publish/
**/models/
**/*.exe
**/*.onnx
**/*.dll
**/*.pdb
**/*.user
**/*.suo
**/*.cache
**/.vs/
**/.vscode/
**/redist/
